      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MESSY AND UNTIDY (4) finished well back at Wentworth Park last time when a 6 length seventh (30.19) but scored five back at this track (29.58). Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Can make amends. CANYA TALKING (8) drawn the outside box and could get a clear run. Was below best last time when 6th and beaten 8 lengths at Wentworth Park (30.10). Goes very well at course and distance boasting three wins. Worth following up. RATTLIN' BYE (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.95) at this track behind Cessnock Curtain in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can feature again. SUNSHINE RHONDA (1) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
